data.description: Spectacular 3 bedroom, 3 bath, 2 car garage, in-ground pool home, with an additional building lot, perfect for investment or added privacy! Embrace the spacious half circular driveway catering to 8 cars, boat & RV! This unique home has been updated from top to bottom with over 2,100 sq.ft  of luxury living and six entryways to the magnificent caged in-ground pool, having over 1,000 sq.ft of expanded full patio! Must see! Delight in the elegant kitchen featuring quartz countertops, under cabinet lighting, pull-out drawers, and premium stainless appliances, overlooking the cozy family room and dinette, all with stunning pool views. Experience an abundance of natural light through arched and triangular windows, enhanced by the allure of colored columns, angular ceilings, and a brand new roof! Unwind in the master bedroom with the most beautiful pool view, a walk-in closet, and luxurious engineered wood plank flooring. Brand new flooring in bedrooms & laundry room! This home offers modern upgrades, including a new roof (2023), newer A/C (2018), newer hot water heater (2021), new range, dishwasher, microwave & disposal (2023), and also a generator hook up on the right side of the home! Enjoy the convenience of a wired security system, keyless entry, auto pool cleaner & complemented by transferable termite protection. Home has been newly painted (inside & out) and professionally landscaped, enhancing the home’s curb appeal. Home is on public water & septic tank (pumped in 2021!) With proximity to Ollies Pond and its scenic surroundings, this property promises an unmatched lifestyle. This amazing home is centrally located with quick access to Hwy. 41/Tamiami Trail (Murdock), El Jobean (776), and Edgewater Dr. Don't miss the opportunity to call this unparalleled oasis home. Call today for your private tour!
